---
title: Turkey and Caramelized Onion Patty Melts with Potato Wedges and Fry Sauce
description: A diner classic with a turkey twist! Juicy turkey patties are slathered with gooey mozzarella and sweet caramelized onions. Grab a seat at the table and prepare your tastebuds!
